data.description: New, new, new! If you like new, you will LOVE this 3 bedroom 2 bath brick home with new roof, wiring, flooring, sheetrock,paint, doors, soffit, HVAC, plumbing, light fixtures, ceiling fans and appliances. The kitchen features new cabinets, appliances and granite countertops with enough space for your dining area. The living area opens to the kitchen for easy entertaining.The kitchen, living area, bathrooms and hallway have new laminate flooring and the bedrooms have new carpet. The lot isjust over an acre with ample yard in the front and back plus a huge 3 bay shop that has new wiring plus an office area. This home is just waiting on a new family to enjoy all of the updates.
